INSERT INTO layerzero_nonces (chain_id, src_eid, nonce_lz, tx_id, updated_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, NOW())
            ON CONFLICT (chain_id, src_eid) 
            DO UPDATE SET 
                nonce_lz = EXCLUDED.nonce_lz,
                tx_id = EXCLUDED.tx_id,
                updated_at = NOW()
